Acoustic Fence 

 Close






 








Polycom Acoustic Fence
Experience premium quality audio without distracting background noise while in the office or on the road.




Polycom Acoustic Fence technology dramatically improves the most important component of the VVX experience - voice clarity by keeping business conversations free from extraneous noises and distractions. 






  Play 

NoiseBlock 

 Close






 








Polycom NoiseBlock Technology
Polycom NoiseBlock technology blocks unwanted noise during video calls from RealPresence Group Series or in a multipoint call on RealPresence Collaboration Server.



Eliminate disruptive noise when you're not speaking. NoiseBlock removes distracting noises between comments—from shuffling papers to typing on a laptop—and enables an uninterrupted flow of ideas.






  Play 

Auto Frame and Zoom 

 Close






 








EagleEye Producer Solutions Feature
See how EagleEye Producer enhances the meeting experience and benefits the business workflow.



Make sure everyone is seen and heard clearly. EagleEye Producer automatically frames and zooms in on the current speaker, no matter where they are in the room. 






