Overview

Crystal-clear audio conversations make meetings productive. Polycom is the industry leader in audio conferencing solutions—and has been for more than 25 years. Our solutions provide superb voice quality, expansive microphone pickup, advanced audio processing, and all the features that make conference calls in Skype for Business environments seem as natural as being in the same room.
Polycom is the only vendor with Skype for Business / Lync interoperable audio conferencing solutions that can meet all your conferencing needs and deliver the lifelike audio quality you expect.

Ensure everyone can be clearly heard, allowing you to focus on the meeting
Deliver 360-degree microphone pickup and other group voice capabilities
Boost productivity with a tightly integrated user experience








RealPresence Trio
The first and only conference phone for group collaboration that is qualified with Skype for Business and Microsoft O365 Cloud PBX powered by Skype for Business Online. 
