Technical Specifications

When making a decision on voice conferencing technology, one name stands above the rest—Polycom.
Why? Because Polycom voice conferencing solutions offer everything you need in a group conferencing solution—high-quality voice, simple deployment and wide interoperability with IP PBXs and Microsoft environments.
Polycom Voice Conferencing Solutions offer:

360-degree microphone pickup and other technology for creating seamless group conversations
Polycom HD Voice and patented Polycom Acoustic Clarity technology—enabling loud, clear, group calls without echoes, dropouts or feedback
A broad selection of Skype for Business, Lync 2010 and Lync 2013 qualified solutions

 






User Benefits

Polycom is the industry leader in audio conferencing solutions. Polycom delivers more Skype for Business/Lync qualified conference phones and speakerphones than any other vendor.

Polycom conference phones are easy to use
Polycom delivers life-like audio that sounds as natural as being in the same room
Echo cancellation and background noise reduction means clearer communications without distractions

 






