Polycom, Inc.
Polycom is the global leader in open standards-based UC&C solutions for voice and video collaboration, trusted by more than 415,000 customers. Polycom solutions are powered by the Polycom® RealPresence® Platform, comprehensive software infrastructure and rich APIs that interoperate with the broadest set of applications and devices for secure face-to-face video collaboration in any environment.









