Polycom VOIP Phones
We offer you a great selection of Polycom VoIP phone systems ranging from 2 lines to 6 lines of operation. These Polycom VOIP phones provide you with up to 10 dedicated hard keys, 1 button access and 3 context sensitive soft keys. Polycom VOIP phones deliver excellent voice quality when paired with a headset.

Polycom VoIP phones / Voice Over Internet Protocol Phones also feature integrated video, voice and web components that allow you to easily connect and conference. With 160x80 graphical LCD display you can view incoming call information in low light conditions. These Polycom VOIP phone models feature one-touch speed dial, message waiting indicator and 3-way conferencing.























































